COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 3:57PM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.4 thousand have died.

In the last day, 282 new infections were reported and 2 deaths. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 43 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 79% have their 1st shot and 50.4% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 7.5 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~19 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ should have the first dose by Nov-10 and fully vaccinated by Aug-17. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
